The ANH (A New Hope) Darth vader chestbox has:
* 3 coin slot red lights
* 1 rectangular red light
* 1 rectangular green light
* 4 rocker switches

Inspired by:
* https://www.pjrc.com/stormtrooper-voice-changer/

The goal of this project is to integrate the following into the chestbox
* Blinking lights
* Voice changer
* Play Imperial March
* Play breathing sounds
* Speakers


Power source:
* 3.7V 2500 mAh LiPo battery
* Adafruit LiPoly charger (https://www.adafruit.com/product/259)
* 3.3V Voltage regulator

Microphone:
* 1 microphone with mono 3.5" audio jack
* 1 female mono 3.5" jack
* Circuit (https://www.pjrc.com/teensy/gui/img/adccircuit.png)
  * 2 47K resistors
  * 1 10K resistor
  * 1 2.2K resistor
  * 2 10 uf capacitors
Connected to pin A2


